Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.39,0:04:01.55,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,yeah boom 着火 no matter what you are
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.64,0:04:04.64,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,照天烧 burn the fire just set on the 火焰
